---
// src/components/SocialProof.astro
---
<section class="bg-[#0e0e0e] py-16 px-6 relative z-10 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-center mb-12 text-white">Depoimentos Reais</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-[#1b1b1b] border-t-2 border-brand-yellow p-6 rounded shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="flex text-brand-yellow mb-4 text-lg">
                    ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
                </div>
                <p class="text-[#e2e2e2] mb-6 italic">"Atendimento impecável, chegaram muito rápido no meio da rodovia quando meu carro ferveu. Super recomendo!"</p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-auto border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white">Ricardo S.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-[#1b1b1b] border-t-2 border-brand-yellow p-6 rounded shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="flex text-brand-yellow mb-4 text-lg">
                    ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
                </div>
                <p class="text-[#e2e2e2] mb-6 italic">"A bateria do meu carro morreu de madrugada e em 25 minutos o Rodrigo já estava no local com uma nova."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-auto border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white">Mariana F.</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[#1b1b1b] border-t-2 border-brand-yellow p-6 rounded shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="flex text-brand-yellow mb-4 text-lg">
                    ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
                </div>
                <p class="text-[#e2e2e2] mb-6 italic">"Meu carro deu pane seca no anel viário, fiquei assustado. O resgate chegou antes do previsto. Profissionais demais."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center mt-auto border-t border-white/10 pt-4">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white">João P.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
